<HEAD>Entertainer Returns to Hospital</HEAD>
<DATELINE>WHITE PLAINS, N.Y. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Entertainer Cab Calloway has returned
to the hospital for treatment of an undisclosed ailment, a
spokeswoman said Friday.
   Calloway, 81, was listed in good condition, but his family has
requested that no information be given out about his ailment, said
Wendy Serkin, speaking for the White Plains Hospital.
