Newcastle upon Tyne in northeast England after Lowery called to see
them Thursday night, the police said. The children disappeared while
their mother, Barbara Lowery, was in the bathroom, according to the
statement.
   Lowery and his wife emigrated to the United States several years
ago, but they separated and she returned to Britain with the
children, police said.
