   Former Defense Secretary Frank C. Carlucci
has been elected to Bell Atlantic Corp.'s board of directors, the
telephone company announced.
   Carlucci's appointment is effective immediately and will run
until he retires, Patty Seif, a Bell Atlantic spokeswoman, said
Thursday.
