Pennsylvania, Diamond State Telephone in Delaware, New Jersey Bell
and the Chesapeake &amp; Potomac Telephone Cos. in the District of
Columbia, Maryland, Virginia and West Virginia Bell.
   The company also owns Bell Atlantic Mobile Telephone; the
international computer-maintenance firm Sorbus, and a commercial
real estate development firm, Bell Atlantic Properties.
