.18 to 166.53. At the American Stock Exchange, the market value
index was up .26 at 324.78.
   On Thursday the Dow Jones industrial average dropped 4.46 to
2,333.75.
   Advancing issues outnumbered declines by about 7 to 6 on the
NYSE, with 755 up, 648 down and 546 unchanged.
   Big Board volume totaled 183.43 million shares, against 215.64
million in the previous session.
